=== Series in topological vector spaces ===
If formula_265 is a topological vector space (TVS) and formula_301 is a (possibly uncountable) family in formula_265 then this family is summable if the limit formula_303 of the net formula_304 exists in formula_246 where formula_235 is the directed set of all finite subsets of formula_203 directed by inclusion formula_238 and formula_309

